Dear Mr John Nash,

The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A has invited you to access the medical information of Ms AZ Patient 1 so you can help manage their health.

Message from The Az 1 TeamCoord

Please consider being my carer

To accept this invitation, click this link:

http://pkb-frontend-9/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2152&temp=pK0Hr0e306

Questions?
  1. Is this secure? Patients Know Best is GDPR-compliant for European patients and HIPAA-compliant for US ones. The UK site is part of the NHS secure network (N3), so it is already built to NHS security standards and approved for usage with any NHS computer.
  2. Do I have to register with the web site? Yes, but registration is free and fast. Please click this link: http://pkb-frontend-9/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2152&temp=pK0Hr0e306
  3. What happens after I register? You can access the records of Ms AZ Patient 1 to use Patients Know Best together securely.

You are receiving this notification because you have been invited as a carer. Once registered, log in and review the people you care for by following this link: "http://pkb-frontend-9/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents"

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

[Date: Wed, 11 Jan 2023 00:19:33 +0000 (UTC) From: Patients Know Best To: john.nash@pkbtest.com Message-ID: <96178852.667.1673396373312@bf4c8e47914d> Subject: The Az 1 TeamCoord would like to share the health record of Ms AZ Patient 1 with you MIME-Version: 1.0 Content-Type: multipart/mixed; boundary="----=_Part_664_1519391485.1673396373308" ------=_Part_664_1519391485.1673396373308 Content-Type: multipart/related; boundary="----=_Part_665_1405535156.1673396373308" ------=_Part_665_1405535156.1673396373308 Content-Type: multipart/alternative; boundary="----=_Part_666_1439776843.1673396373308" ------=_Part_666_1439776843.1673396373308 Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8 Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit Dear Mr John Nash, The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A has invited you to access the medical information of Ms AZ Patient 1 so you can help manage their health. ---------- Message from The Az 1 TeamCoord Please consider being my carer ---------- To accept this invitation, click this link: http://pkb-frontend-9/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2152&temp=pK0Hr0e306 Questions? 1. Is this secure? Patients Know Best is GDPR-compliant for European patients and HIPAA-compliant for US ones. The UK site is part of the NHS secure network (N3), so it is already built to NHS security standards and approved for usage with any NHS computer. 2. Do I have to register with the web site? Yes, but registration is free and fast. Please click this link: http://pkb-frontend-9/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2152&temp=pK0Hr0e306 3. What happens after I register? You can access the records of Ms AZ Patient 1 to use Patients Know Best together securely. You are receiving this notification because you have been invited as a carer. Once registered, log in and review the people you care for by following this link: http://pkb-frontend-9/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Yours, Patients Know Best Help Team w: www.patientsknowbest.com/contact-us e: help@pkbtest.com ------=_Part_666_1439776843.1673396373308 Content-Type: text/html;charset=UTF-8 Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit

Dear Mr John Nash,

The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A has invited you to access the medical information of Ms AZ Patient 1 so you can help manage their health.

Message from The Az 1 TeamCoord

Please consider being my carer

To accept this invitation, click this link:

http://pkb-frontend-9/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2152&temp=pK0Hr0e306

Questions?
  1. Is this secure? Patients Know Best is GDPR-compliant for European patients and HIPAA-compliant for US ones. The UK site is part of the NHS secure network (N3), so it is already built to NHS security standards and approved for usage with any NHS computer.
  2. Do I have to register with the web site? Yes, but registration is free and fast. Please click this link: http://pkb-frontend-9/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2152&temp=pK0Hr0e306
  3. What happens after I register? You can access the records of Ms AZ Patient 1 to use Patients Know Best together securely.

You are receiving this notification because you have been invited as a carer. Once registered, log in and review the people you care for by following this link: "http://pkb-frontend-9/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents"

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
